data.description: Great opportunity to get out in the country on your own 3+ acre parcel. Home features over 2,700 sq ft. of finished living space, new stainless steel kitchen appliances, refinished hardwood floors, new flooring in the kitchen and mud room. Wood burning fireplace in the living room. Many updates including trim / hardware / new carpet in Owner's suite and great room. Plenty of room for your hobbies and collections with a 24x30 detached garage and a 30x40 pole building. Centerburg school district, Don't let this one pass you by.
